# RFM Customer Segmentation

A reproducible, end-to-end RFM (Recency, Frequency, Monetary) analysis pipeline  
for an international retail company, with synthetic data generation.

## Project Structure

    .
    ├── .gitignore
    ├── pyproject.toml
    ├── README.md
    ├── .venv/
    ├── data/
    │   ├── raw/
    │   └── processed/
    ├── sql/
    │   ├── create_tables.sql
    │   └── queries/
    ├── src/
    │   ├── __init__.py
    │   ├── synthetic_data.py
    │   ├── data_engineering.py
    │   ├── rfm.py
    │   └── utils.py
    ├── notebooks/
    │   └── 01_EDA.ipynb
    └── tests/
        └── test_rfm.py

